  "original_title": "\u0d91\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dd9\u0db3 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dda\u0da2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka is included in England's trade package",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign media reported that the British government has decided to include Sri Lanka in the new trade scheme for developing countries introduced by Britain instead of the European Union's GSP concession.",
        "Sri Lanka will continue to benefit from the fact that more than 80 percent of Sri Lanka's exports to Britain are already duty-free and that Sri Lanka's food and textile exports to Britain will continue to benefit from the inclusion of Sri Lanka in the new trade scheme for developing countries introduced by Britain. Sarah Hulton, the British High Commissioner in Sri Lanka, said that about 150 types of additional products will be entitled to a cut or concession in Britain's import duties.",
        "This means that baby clothes exported from Sri Lanka will receive a 12 percent reduction in import duties in Britain.",
        "Foreign media said that 65 developing countries are included in this scheme.",
        "The foreign media pointed out that this scheme will provide easier access to Britain for exports from developing countries.",
        "The British government pointed out that the new trade scheme for developing countries will remove or cut import duties imposed from season to season, for example, cucumbers can be exported to Britain without import duties in the winter season.",
        "Foreign media pointed out that Sri Lanka and seven other countries will be included in a special scheme operating under the new trade scheme for developing countries in Britain, whereby two-thirds of Sri Lanka's export products will not be subject to import duties."
      ],
